data.description: This home checks all the boxes. This stunning country home gives you the space you desire while still close to schools and city amenities. Situated on 3.62 acres this home features not one, but two 40x50 insulated shops. The first shop is heated and cooled and features an extra living quarters/man cave. The second shop is heated and provides ample work space. One shop to work, and one shop to play. Between both shops there is space for RV parking. Outside provides ample driveway and parking space. Not only do you have acreage, but you also have a large fenced back yard with mature landscape. If you are already drooling over the outside amenities, don't worry the inside does not disappoint either. Kitchen features beautiful granite counter tops and cabinetry while overlooking the living and dinning rooms. 4 ample sized bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Main home also features a 2 car garage that you can actually park in since you have 2 shops for storage. Call today
